==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Collagen
<hw>Col"la*gen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>ko`lla</grk> glue + <ets>-gen</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.
Chem.)</fld> <def>The chemical basis of ordinary connective tissue, as
of tendons or sinews and of bone. On being boiled in water it becomes
gelatin or glue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Collagenous</ent>⟦br⟧
